data.title: Vince Staples x Bad Rabbits -- "Made" - In The Studio
data.description:
Stream and download "Made" 

"Made" is the first single off of the second Converse CONS compilation, CONS EP Vol. 2, coming Summer/Fall of 2014. The song was recorded at Sunset Sound Recording Studio in Los Angeles, CA and Chicago Recording Company in Chicago Illinois. 

Produced by: Bad Rabbits 
Music by: Bad Rabbits & Vince Staples
Lyrics by: Bad Rabbits & Vince Staples
Vocals by: Bad Rabbits & Vince Staples
Talkbox Vocals by: Sergio Selim

data.title: CONVERSE CLASH WALL PARIS
data.description:
For two weeks, French artists Alëxone and Supakitch took over a historical house on the 'Canal de l'Ourcq' in Paris.

Inspired by ideas submitted by fans on Twitter, the two friends painted the house inside and out to amazing effect: A unique piece of art open for all to discover until the end of August.

data.title: Converse CONS Project - Lisboa
data.description: CONS Project Lisboa saw Converse CONS skateboarders Javier Mendizabal, Remy Taveira, Carlos Cardenosa, Felipe Bartolome, Octavio Barrera and more collaborate with artists, musicians and photographers to express their creativity in a unique space in downtown Lisbon. A series of photography workshops and art installations gave local youth a new creative home for 5 weeks this April and May.
